Depends: e2fsprogs, fdisk, ca-certificates, util-linux, jq, curl, busybox-static, dropbear-bin, wpasupplicant, iw, firmware-brcm80211
Description: Raspberry Pi self-update tool
 Build an initramfs that can download, flash, and verify a new OS image
 on a Raspberry Pi, preserving home directories and SSH keys.
